<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Verify Your Email with OTP</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }
        .otp-container {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b 0%, #ee5a24 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .instructions {
            background: #e8f4f8;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .expiry {
            background: #fff3cd;
            color: #856404;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>🔐 Verify Your Email Address</h1>
        <p>One-Time Password Required</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
        <p>Thank you for signing up for {{appName}}! To complete your registration and start connecting with other developers, please use the OTP code below to verify your email address.</p>
        
        <div class="otp-container">
            {{otp}}
        </div>
        
        <div class="instructions">
            <h3>📋 How to Verify:</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Return to the {{appName}} app</li>
                <li>Enter the OTP code: <strong>{{otp}}</strong></li>
                <li>Click "Verify Email"</li>
                <li>Start your dating journey! 🚀</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        
        <div class="expiry">
            ⏰ <strong>Important:</strong> This OTP will expire in <strong>10 minutes</strong> for security reasons. If you didn't request this verification, please ignore this email.
        </div>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or didn't request this verification, please contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>If you didn't create an account with {{appName}}, please ignore this email.</p>
        <p>© 2024 {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>Need help? Contact us at {{supportEmail}}</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
